## install docker
`sudo apt  install docker.io`

## install docker-compose

`sudo apt  install docker-compose`

`sudo chmod 666 /var/run/docker.sock`

# Run the app
docker-compose up --build 

target_1    | App listening on port 9997
splitter_1  | App listening on port 9998


Run `docker-compose scale target=2` observe the second instance come up

target_2    | App listening on port 9997
